Oita Prefecture announced on the 25th that it has confirmed the identity of the body found on the Oita River in Yufu City on the 23rd with Watanabe Kenta (28), a ryokan company who had been missing due to torrential rains, in Yuhira, Yufuin-cho, Yufuin.
